    correctAnswer:"File a complaint against unfair trade practices and get compensation through consumer courts",
    difficulty:"easy",
    explanation:"Right to Seek Redressal gives consumers the legal right to get compensation for unfair trade practices, defective goods, or deficient services through the 3-tier consumer court system.",
    solutionSteps:["Consumer exploited → can file complaint","District Forum (up to ₹1 crore)","State Commission (up to ₹10 crore)","National Commission (above ₹10 crore)"],
